# Tenant .gitignore -- INVERSION (DP3 gitignore_profile=tenant).
# COMMITTED (the tenant's identity + activated taxonomy are version-controlled):
#   brand/  overlay/  brand/tenant_config.json  .cex/kinds_meta.json  archetypes/builders/
#   .cex/brand/  .cex/overlays/  (the brain GLOBAL read-path mirror -- residual #4)
# IGNORED (secrets + ephemeral runtime + build output):
secrets/
.env
.env.*
# ...but DO ship the app env TEMPLATES (offline-render defaults on clone); only the real
# .env / .env.local stay ignored above.
!**/.env.example
**/runtime/
# memory is scoped to .cex/ so this pattern never shadows the vendored cexai SDK package
# cexai/cexai/memory/ (a real, committed source dir -- NOT ephemeral runtime memory).
.cex/**/memory/
.cex/runtime/
.cex/cache/
.cex/distill/
.cex/total_index/
node_modules/
.next/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.tsbuildinfo
